Whats New:

- Added a nice sun (which filled the skybox and stopped a leak)
- Added more crates all of which are breakable
- i extended the ladder so you can escape form the annoying ledges
- added a thin layer of water in the pit to stop tking
- added a car and 4 explosive barrels in the pit for effect
- added mroe water barrels
- upgraded the bunkers in spawns and retextured the windows
- fixed the awp spawn

- I hope you all like it this 'wont' be my last version i am planning on making one more. so keep tuned

- please give me your thoughts ,ratings , ect ect on what you think of the map
